consul; steup required

step 1:download consul from offical website
step2: from consul folder run server using 

consul agent -server  -bootstrap-expect=1 -data-dir=consul-data -ui -bind=<IP address>

now after running you can see consul info

step 3:http://localhost:8500--->to access consul ui

step 4:go to kv tab

step5:  create key--->folder-name/application-name/my.username
and provide value---->12345

step5:if you update password you can see changes

